headline: 3 Big Reasons to Love Cencora (COR)
summary: Since July 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 97.8%. But one standout stock has doubled the market - over the past five years, Cencora has surged 196% to $296 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 31.7% in the last six months, beating the S&P by 26.1%.
